value: 5084 - Industrial Machinery and Equipment Summary > KEYSIGHT TECHNOLOGIES AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover industrial machinery and equipment. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. KEYSIGHT TECHNOLOGIES AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is headquartered in Mulgrave, Victoria. It is headed by director & general manager Keith Noel Baucke. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $36.24 million. Its net profit totalled $2.82 million. KEYSIGHT TECHNOLOGIES AUSTRALIA PTY LTD forms part of the wholesale trade industry sector. Key Personnel > No key personnel were found for the selected company.
